{"tid":329974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支爆累到港爆] 陳雲：大家好快不必供樓","createTime":"2017-07-20T19:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T23:52:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"202cf66a97b12c8f3183eb1f8bf54ef9043afc8a","tid":329974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:40:57.000Z","msg":"陳雲：大家好快不必供樓，因為香港不久會有銀行因為過度借貸予中國而倒閉，房產證明書又抵押了給銀行，一時之間不知由誰接管（可能由仍未宣布破產的共資銀行承擔），你想入錢供樓都無從入手，入了錢的新銀行又隨時宣布破產，好多供樓一族會患上抑鬱病，到時好多香港人因為無法繼續供樓而失去人生目標，跳樓自殺。"},{"pid":"e87a155a33db9e795b5a052308f088054d14d162","tid":329974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:43:59.000Z","msg":"阿嬸比陳雲永續基本法呃，賣左層樓，而家睇住樓價升 <br />\n<br />\n 我仲記得陳雲上年話2047大限將到, 好多銀行做唔到按揭 <br />\n到時樓價大趺, 結果樓價升到宜家 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6736372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6736372&d=dexsi9N9yaZrY9yHU43kTAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c1db88c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6736372</a>"},{"pid":"f82b69c78d3b32a4612f268782863bb0c261ab98","tid":329974,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:48:40.000Z","msg":"On L9 <br />\n<br />\n陳魂連供樓/借貸都攪唔清楚<br />\n偷post前睇一睇吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed2318a29d9caed4a750b5d836a72fc2e605171","tid":329974,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:29:07.000Z","msg":"唔記得食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f7c56f972d8e6c91da547a532540390c96db19","tid":329974,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:30:43.000Z","msg":"自己果層賣左未"},{"pid":"2b01277fc976ffec9081b58ee2edd8cb8e2991af","tid":329974,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:36:16.000Z","msg":"銀行破產唔代表你唔洗邏<br />\n會有法庭委託嘅清盤人掌管銀行<br />\n